# This repo holds the RAW contract corpus (source of truth) plus the offline
# docling extraction tool. The retired Python/Mongo ingestion+pricing pass has
# been removed (see safaris-knowledgebase ADR-0001 / ADR-0003) and stays out.
#
# EXCEPTION: docling is a permitted offline parse tool (ADR-0003 clause 4).
# Its script (extract.py), requirements.txt, EXTRACTION.md, and the generated
# artifacts/ ARE tracked — artifacts/ is the whole point of the Mac-mini handoff.

# Secrets — never commit
.env
.env.*

# Python runtime cruft (NOT the extraction tool itself)
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*_env/
venv/
.venv/

# docling model cache, if pointed at this tree
.docling/
models/

# Generated reports from the retired tooling
ingestion/reports/
